@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@authToken = {{auth_token}}

### Create Pet (with Cloudinary URLs)
POST {{baseUrl}}/pets
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Fluffy",
  "species": "dog",
  "breed": "Golden Retriever",
  "age": 24,
  "gender": "female",
  "healthNotes": "Up to date on vaccinations",
  "photoUrl": "https://res.cloudinary.com/your-cloud/image/upload/v123/pets/fluffy-main.jpg",
  "photoUrls": [
    "https://res.cloudinary.com/your-cloud/image/upload/v123/pets/fluffy-1.jpg",
    "https://res.cloudinary.com/your-cloud/image/upload/v123/pets/fluffy-2.jpg"
  ],
  "isAvailable": true
}

###
### Get All Pets (search)
GET {{baseUrl}}/pets?species=dog&limit=10&offset=0

###
### Get Single Pet
GET {{baseUrl}}/pets/1

